{"tid":414392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊岳橋: 對國務院委任張曉明出任港澳辦主任感到失望","createTime":"2017-09-26T07:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T07:59:20.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"154b7d1a1a1099deb9b0fc32015d58e5b4322589","tid":414392,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"公民黨黨魁楊岳橋對任命感到非常失望，張曉明出任港澳辦主任明顯是「升職」，顯示中央政府滿意他過去5年在港的工作。楊岳橋說，張曉明上任後發生佔領運動，過去幾年社會有港獨討論，張曉明是責無旁貸。楊岳橋擔心，任命是否意味中央對香港撕裂的情況視而不見，他對未來香港情況不感樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1355484-20170922.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1355484-20170922.htm&d=hq1Tv1DQFqCq6TPm3S9dwtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=40ef961f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1355484-20170922.htm&h=e38dbde4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1355484-20170922.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ae9577bb392ddbbb909c282fbc0bf307d361b0a9","tid":414392,"uid":64056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公民黨黨魁楊岳橋對任命感到非常失望，張曉明出任港澳辦主任明顯是「升職」，顯示中央政府滿意他過去5年在港的工作。楊岳橋說，張曉明上任後發生佔領運動，過去幾年社會有港獨討論，張曉明是責無旁貸。楊岳橋擔心，任命是否意味中央對香港撕裂的情況視而不見，他對未來香港情況不感樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1355484-20170922.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1355484-20170922.htm&d=hq1Tv1DQFqCq6TPm3S9dwtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=40ef961f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1355484-20170922.htm&h=e38dbde4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1355484-20170922.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n公民黨擁護南亞人侵食我地本地人又係咪撕裂緊香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}